snippet.title: Goldfinger N64 Hack: Intro & 1st level
snippet.description:
This is a first run through the first level of the recently released Goldfinger game for the N64. It is a hack of 007 Goldeneye and here is some gameplay for it.

Some bits have been edited. For example, there is a black loading screen just before the "Ramirez Drug Cartel, Mexico" scene appears. Also, a buzzing sound from my recording equipment has been edited out a bit.

This was recorded on real N64 hardware.
